<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf00e53c0-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s7489"><num value="7489">§ 7489.</num><heading> Relation to other programs</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Nothing in this subchapter preempts or supersedes any other program relating to popcorn promotion organized and operated under the laws of the United States or any State.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf00e53c1-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/127/tV/s580">Pub. L. 104–127, title V, § 580</ref>, <date date="1996-04-04">Apr. 4, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/1083">110 Stat. 1083</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
